17
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:38,440
Miss.

18
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,417
Miss.

19
00:01:40,441 --> 00:01:41,760
You're finally back.

20
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,240
Miss? What are you talking about?

21
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:45,456
You've got the wrong person.

22
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:47,776
Miss, please don't joke like that.

23
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:49,896
We have been looking for you for days.

24
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,736
Ever since the Boss passed away,

25
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:52,736
