27
00:01:53,561 --> 00:01:54,960
The gang is in chaos now.

28
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:57,096
Only you can take charge.

29
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:58,880
I don't understand
what you're talking about.

30
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:00,640
I'm a representative of Longxing Group.

31
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,000
My name is An Ning.

32
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:03,160
An Ning?

33
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:05,120
Longxing Group?

34
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,200
An Ning...

35
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:16,456
Tell me, in this world,

36
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:18,760
