that much alike?

37
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:20,656
Exactly the same.

38
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:22,936
No wonder Song Pa asked me to
handle the negotiation.

39
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,696
He must've noticed this beforehand.

40
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:26,760
So he's doubting my identity.

41
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,976
Just two similar faces.

42
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,096
No big deal.

43
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,176
Besides,

44
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:35,360
what can one photo prove?

45
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,776
Bring me the Young Lady's tablet.

46
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,800
Yes.

47
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:46,920
Jiang Meng,

48
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,976
the moment she blows her cover,

49
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:49,977
show no mercy.

50
00:02:50,001 --> 00:02:51,080
Shoot to kill right away.

51
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,560
Mom.

52
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,856
But suppose she

53
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:02,696
really is Ye Ying.

54
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:04,056
Even if she's dead,

55
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,720
