58
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:12,056
But won't the Qingyun Gang

59
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,320
want revenge?

60
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:16,296
She died on their turf.

61
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:18,080
None of our business.

62
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:20,336
They dared to take over our territory.

63
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:22,136
They're definitely swallowing this loss.

64
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,760
Mom, you always think ahead.

65
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,656
Once that sneaky woman is gone,

66
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,016
you'll save so much trouble.

67
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,040
Don't worry.

68
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,896
If you do a big favor this time,

69
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:32,776
you'll get a share of
her holdings for sure.

70
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,920
Thank you, Mom.

71
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:38,257
Inspector.

72
00:03:38,281 --> 00:03:39,656
You're gonna save that An Ning

73
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,696
or Ye Ying, are you?

74
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:42,056
This is a Song family matter.

75
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:42,976
I think, professionally and personally,

76
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,857
you shouldn't get involved in it.

77
00:03:43,881 --> 00:03:45,296
It's exactly because
her identity isn't confirmed

78
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,616
that we need to keep observing her.

79
00:03:46,640 --> 00:03:47,936
If she really turns out to be our target,

80
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,560
then one mistake could ruin everything.

81
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:53,456
This tablet

82
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:55,216
only registers
the Young Lady's fingerprint.

83
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,096
She's the only one who can open it.

84
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:59,480
Want me to believe your identity?

85
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,320
Prove it.

86
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,240
No way.

87
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:37,560
I couldn't have mistaken it.

88
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:41,536
Just as I thought.

89
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:43,320
Verify identity through fingerprint.

90
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,200
However,

91
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,616
I've already replaced all the clues

92
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:48,800
