93
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:52,280
The setup has been done.

94
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:53,760
Ye Ying.

95
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,480
Now, let's see how you make your move.

96
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,440
Qingyun Gang's being so tricky.

97
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,696
Are you trying to stall for time?

98
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,040
And refuse to give the dock back?

99
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:10,040
Since you're not the Young Lady,

100
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,976
then I won't

101
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,120
