123
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,456
Exactly.

124
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:02,920
And I'll bring all the guys

125
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,936
to patronize you every day.

126
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:05,857
Make sure you live

127
00:06:05,881 --> 00:06:07,280
