134
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:20,776
Alright.

135
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:21,576
Guys.

136
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,600
Get her!

137
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:29,640
Stop,

138
00:06:34,490 --> 00:06:38,600
